comments: Gobert (UTA) makes marginal contact with Doncic's (DAL) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (UTA) sets the pick in Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Ingles (UTA) makes incidental contact with Doncic's (DAL) hand after cleanly dislodging the ball during the drive.
Doncic (DAL) makes marginal contact with O'Neale (UTA) that does not prevent him from gathering the loose ball.
Doncic (DAL) swipes down and makes contact to Mitchell's (UTA) arm during his shot attempt.
Wright (DAL) sets the screen in Ingles's (UTA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Gobert (UTA) makes marginal contact with Wright's (DAL) body before cleanly blocking his driving shot attempt.
Curry (DAL) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
Finney-Smith (DAL) makes contact with Mitchell's (UTA) shoulder after Mitchell gathers with his hand under the ball during the driving shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) makes marginal contact with Finney-Smith's (DAL) body during his shooting motion on the play at the basket.
Gobert (UTA) and Finney-Smith (DAL) make incidental contact during the rebound.
Porzingis (DAL) commits a take foul on Gobert (UTA).
Mitchell (UTA) and Curry (DAL) briefly engage and separate during the inbound.
Ingles (UTA) legally contests Porzingis's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
